{"title":"Java 與 Kotlin 對照筆記","uid":"ec689fac42391847d1970b8ad306d112","slug":"java-kotlin-comparison-notes","date":"2022-12-21T04:00:50.000Z","updated":"2023-01-30T13:00:49.651Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/java-kotlin-comparison-notes.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.com/dkq1jBA.jpg","content":"<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dkq1jBA.jpg\" alt=\"cover\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"存取修飾子\"><a href=\"#存取修飾子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"存取修飾子\"></a>存取修飾子</h1><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>修飾子 <br> Access Modifiers</th>\n<th>Java</th>\n<th>Kotlin</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>public</code></td>\n<td>所有類可存取 <br> All classes can be accessed</td>\n<td>所有類可存取 <strong>（預設）</strong> <br> All classes can be accessed <strong>(default)</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>private</code></td>\n<td>當前類可存取 <br> Only the current class can be accessed</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>protected</code></td>\n<td>當前類、子類、同一套件路徑下的類可存取 <br> Only the current class, sub-class and the classes that belong to the same package can be accessed</td>\n<td>當前類、子類可存取 <br> Only the current class, sub-class can be accessed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>default</code></td>\n<td>同一套件路徑下的類可存取 <strong>（預設）</strong> <br> Only the classes that belong to the same package can be accessed <strong>(default)</strong></td>\n<td>無 <br> None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>internal</code></td>\n<td>無 <br> None</td>\n<td>同一模組中的類可存取 <br> Only the class that is inside the same module can be accessed</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"決策邏輯\"><a href=\"#決策邏輯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"決策邏輯\"></a>決策邏輯</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"if-else\"><a href=\"#if-else\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if else\"></a>if else</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">if (x &gt; y) z &#x3D; x;\nelse z &#x3D; y;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">z &#x3D; if (x &gt; y) x else y</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"switch-when\"><a href=\"#switch-when\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"switch? when?\"></a>switch? when?</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">switch (x) &#123;\n    case 1: doSomething() break;\n    case 2: doSomething() break;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;...\n    default: doSomething();\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">when (x) &#123;\n    1 -&gt; doSomething()\n    2 -&gt; doSomething()\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;...\n    else -&gt; doSomething()\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"數據類\"><a href=\"#數據類\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"數據類\"></a>數據類</h1><p>要是實現數據類的話，我高度建議使用 Kotlin 語法的數據類結構 <code>data class</code> ，因為它<strong>簡化並內置了</strong> Java 數據類的 <code>getXXX()</code>、<code>setXXX()</code>、<code>toString()</code>、<code>hashCode()</code> 等方法。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Java</span></div><code class=\"language-java\">public class Person &#123;\n    private String name;\n\n    public Person(String name) &#123;\n        this.name &#x3D; name;\n    &#125;\n\n    public void setName(String name) &#123;\n        this.name &#x3D; name;\n    &#125;\n\n    public String getName() &#123;\n        return name;\n    &#125;\n&#125;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; to use\nPerson person &#x3D; new Person(&quot;Steve&quot;);\nSystem.out.println(person.getName());</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-kotlin\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>Kotlin</span></div><code class=\"language-kotlin\">data class Person(val name: String)\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; to use\nval person &#x3D; Person(&quot;Steve&quot;)\nprintln(person.name)</code></pre>","text":" 修飾子 Access Modifiers Java Kotlin 所有類可存取 All classes can be accessed 所有類可存取 （預設） All classes can be accessed (default) 當前類可存取 Only the curre...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":10,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Kotlin","slug":"Kotlin","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Kotlin.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96%E4%BF%AE%E9%A3%BE%E5%AD%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">存取修飾子</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B1%BA%E7%AD%96%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">決策邏輯</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#if-else\"><span class=\"toc-text\">if else</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#switch-when\"><span class=\"toc-text\">switch? when?</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%9E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">數據類</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"http://bit.ly/3WWvvfn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"youtube":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-youtube","link":"https://bit.ly/3C9RlUL"},"facebook":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-facebook","link":null},"instagram":{"icon":"fa-brands fa-instagram","link":null}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"利用 Hexo 建立 GitHub 寄存網誌","uid":"a990d8c2eefbb26d914d318577aa9256","slug":"hexo-create-blog","date":"2022-12-23T23:53:52.000Z","updated":"2023-01-28T03:46:15.063Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-create-blog.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.imgur.co